What you need to know:  Binance Charity said the fund is to provide relief to the families of eight victims who passed away. The cash, the organisation said in a statement on its website, will aid towards funeral costs and living expenses following the deaths of their loved ones.“As one of the sponsors of the AFCON 2021 tournaments and as humans, it was an extremely heartbreaking incident and we want to do our part to help the victims' families,” said Helen Hai, head of Binance Charity.